<p><iframe allowfullscreen="" src="https://v.qq.com/iframe/preview.html?width=500&amp;height=375&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=k072438fipo"></iframe></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>《变迁》第五集：《</strong><strong>担当</strong><strong>》</strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p>